ca.ubc.cs.cpsc211.photo
Class RichardTest

java.lang.Object
  ca.ubc.cs.cpsc211.photo.RichardTest

public class RichardTest
extends java.lang.Object

NOTE these tests were moved from package ca.ubc.cs.cpsc211.test into ca.ubc.cs.cpsc211.photo to allow testing to access package level methods that introduce synchronization errors for tag - photo associations to test resynchronization methods. added whitebox test cases over and above provided test cases, particularly concerned about Tag to Photo association since it is duplicated between (photos pointing to tags) and (tags pointing to photos). Implemenetation placed user interfaces on the photo side so that calls to photo to update tag association, automatically notified Tag to update its photo collection. There is vulnerabilty to loss of synch if client code calls any Tag association methods directly rather than using photo methods. added two synch methods in case there is a mismatch. PhotoManager.writePhotoPointersToTag is from Photo information to Tag. TagManager.writeTagPointersToPhotos is from tag to photo. Both must be run for two way synch.

Author:
rlum

testRemoveTagAfterPhotoTag

public void testRemoveTagAfterPhotoTag()
Extension above the removeTagTest. What if we removeTag after the tag has been assigned to several Photo. The Tag should no longer be in TagManager but also all photos that pointed to that tag should also no longer reference the tag since it no longer should exist. This test confirms that removing a Tag from the tagManager also removes l photo references to that tag.

testSynchFrTagToPhotoAssociations

public void testSynchFrTagToPhotoAssociations()
test the ability to write the photo/tag association information from the Tag information onto Photos view of associations Uses package access methods to force a mismatch between Photo view of Tag-Photo associations and then write the Tag view of the associations onto the Photos.

testSynchFrPhotoToTagAssociations

public void testSynchFrPhotoToTagAssociations()
test the ability to write a the photo/tag association information from the Photo information onto Tags view of associations. Uses package access methods to force a mismatch between Photo view of Tag-Photo associations and then write the Photo view of the associations onto the Tags.
